WEBVTT

00:08:25.172 --> 00:08:30.434
(Applause)

00:08:30.982 --> 00:08:32.501
Our students

00:08:33.610 --> 00:08:36.411
are meant to go and change the world.

00:08:37.498 --> 00:08:41.688
They will come from all over --
it's a global university --

00:08:41.712 --> 00:08:44.903
and will get the medical
education for free

00:08:44.927 --> 00:08:46.904
at one condition:

00:08:46.928 --> 00:08:50.975
they have to serve the vulnerable
across the world

00:08:50.999 --> 00:08:53.046
during six to nine years.

00:08:53.070 --> 00:08:56.585
They will keep the salary
for themselves and their families

00:08:56.609 --> 00:09:00.688
but turn the education we give
in quality clinical services,